WEBVTT

01:35.900 --> 01:40.980
=Love Beyond the Grave=
(Adapted from the novel by Li Qingran)

01:41.260 --> 01:43.980
=Episode 5=

01:52.110 --> 01:53.080
- Drink!
- Bottoms up.

01:55.140 --> 01:55.990
What a thrill.

01:55.990 --> 01:56.870
What a real thrill.

01:56.880 --> 01:58.190
That battle was truly a thrill.

01:58.360 --> 01:59.220
Truly a thrill.

01:59.220 --> 02:00.270
Come, brothers, drink up.

02:00.630 --> 02:01.470
Come on, drink.

02:02.030 --> 02:03.110
We won today's battle

02:04.270 --> 02:05.580
thanks to Miss He's strategy.

02:06.700 --> 02:07.970
She deserves the greatest merit.

02:08.620 --> 02:09.620
Come, brothers.

02:10.230 --> 02:11.580
A toast to Miss He.

02:11.580 --> 02:13.270
- Come on.
- Cheers.

02:13.700 --> 02:15.300
A toast to Miss He.

02:23.950 --> 02:24.830
General,

02:24.830 --> 02:25.830
how did you know

02:25.830 --> 02:27.790
the Fenglai Force would raid tonight?

02:28.020 --> 02:28.860
Very simple.

02:29.740 --> 02:30.700
Because there is

02:32.900 --> 02:33.740
a spy among us.

02:36.620 --> 02:37.460
What?

02:39.110 --> 02:40.270
We told everyone we'd blow up

02:40.270 --> 02:41.580
the Guanhe River tomorrow.

02:42.110 --> 02:43.550
The spy passed the word out.

02:44.350 --> 02:45.959
So, Fenglai would launch a sneak attack

02:45.970 --> 02:46.630
before then.

02:47.580 --> 02:48.740
They had to ready the troops,

02:50.110 --> 02:51.333
so tonight is the best chance.

02:53.070 --> 02:53.910
Who?

02:54.950 --> 02:56.700
Such nerve.

02:57.390 --> 02:58.740
To collude with the enemy army?

02:59.550 --> 03:00.580
Once I find him,

03:00.580 --> 03:01.700
I'll skin him alive.

03:02.550 --> 03:03.390
Commandant Wu,

03:03.950 --> 03:04.990
as for finding the spy,

03:05.700 --> 03:06.840
we need to plan it carefully.

03:07.510 --> 03:08.460
Right now,

03:08.460 --> 03:09.880
we must prepare the city's defenses.

03:10.860 --> 03:11.700
Based on the timing,

03:12.670 --> 03:13.550
Awo'erqi will soon

03:13.550 --> 03:14.550
arrive in Shuozhou.

03:47.670 --> 03:48.510
Simu.

03:49.900 --> 03:50.950
This spell

03:51.140 --> 03:52.950
can help you borrow the five senses

03:52.950 --> 03:53.860
from the spell bearer.

03:54.830 --> 03:56.620
Then you can feel this world.

04:25.860 --> 04:26.700
Miss He,

04:27.620 --> 04:28.710
you seem

04:29.710 --> 04:30.723
a little different today.

04:37.110 --> 04:38.230
I made it back alive.

04:38.860 --> 04:39.990
I fear that disappointed you.

04:40.420 --> 04:41.550
Are you upset?

04:48.820 --> 04:49.740
You jest, General.

04:51.110 --> 04:52.380
I only wish you

04:53.350 --> 04:54.740
good fortune from now on.

05:16.470 --> 05:17.550
(My spell bearer,)

05:18.740 --> 05:20.030
(from this moment on,)

05:21.180 --> 05:22.740
(you must not die.)

05:37.820 --> 05:38.990
Tabai blew up the Guanhe River.

05:39.620 --> 05:40.470
Fenglai was hit hard.

05:44.500 --> 05:48.300
(Awo'erqi, Marshal of Hulan Force,
North Chong)

05:50.110 --> 05:51.110
Fenglai.

05:51.820 --> 05:53.030
That useless fool.

06:06.670 --> 06:08.420
(Great Liang's main force is in Yuzhou,)

06:08.420 --> 06:10.380
(Yuzhou)
(fighting with the Fenglai Force.)

06:10.790 --> 06:12.560
(Liang)
(The Tabai Army that took Shuozhou)

06:12.620 --> 06:13.780
(is left without support.)

06:14.220 --> 06:15.140
(At this moment,)

06:15.140 --> 06:16.060
(Awo'erqi)

06:16.220 --> 06:18.060
(is leading an army of 200,000)

06:18.260 --> 06:20.700
(right toward Shuozhou.)

06:33.380 --> 06:34.320
Awo'erqi is now leading

06:34.740 --> 06:35.719
his army to our borders.

06:36.580 --> 06:37.980
Shuozhou now stands cut off.

06:39.100 --> 06:40.580
Now that we have retaken Shuozhou,

06:41.380 --> 06:42.620
we will stand or fall with it.

06:43.100 --> 06:43.940
Rest easy, General.

06:44.660 --> 06:45.700
Shuozhou is vital ground.

06:46.300 --> 06:48.180
I will hold it to the end.

06:48.740 --> 06:49.580
Commandant Wu,

06:49.820 --> 06:50.980
uphold the walls.

06:51.580 --> 06:52.420
Yes.

06:52.620 --> 06:53.460
Meng Wan, Qingsheng,

06:53.940 --> 06:54.860
go find

06:54.860 --> 06:55.900
the best at eavesdropping.

06:56.300 --> 06:57.140
Yes, General.

06:57.340 --> 06:58.180
Captain Han,

06:58.820 --> 07:00.100
you're in charge of city patrols.

07:00.580 --> 07:02.180
Keep the townsfolk safe at all costs.

07:02.700 --> 07:03.660
Yes.

07:03.660 --> 07:04.500
Report!

07:05.460 --> 07:06.300
General,

07:06.540 --> 07:07.686
the military provisions

07:07.697 --> 07:08.846
sent by Marshal Qin are here.

07:16.620 --> 07:18.500
A full 30,000 dan of grain!

07:19.100 --> 07:21.100
Marshal Qin truly values good men.

07:21.940 --> 07:23.660
He went to great lengths to send it.

07:24.100 --> 07:24.940
Now,

07:25.100 --> 07:26.580
even if we fall on the battlefield,

07:27.300 --> 07:28.380
we can at least

07:28.380 --> 07:29.740
eat our fill before we go.

07:43.100 --> 07:44.140
They're all empty shells.

07:50.860 --> 07:52.220
Who did this?

07:52.980 --> 07:53.820
Who else could it be?

07:54.340 --> 07:55.495
Marshal Qin, known for caring

07:55.506 --> 07:56.260
for the troops.

07:57.740 --> 07:58.580
Impossible.

08:00.020 --> 08:00.860
No way.

08:01.620 --> 08:02.740
We risk our lives

08:02.740 --> 08:04.380
to guard home and country.

08:04.780 --> 08:06.220
Marshal Qin would never do this.

08:06.660 --> 08:08.180
You've long stayed at the border,

08:08.580 --> 08:10.180
but you should know the strife

08:10.820 --> 08:12.475
between Duke Pei,
Marshal Qin's superior,

08:12.486 --> 08:13.220
and Chancellor Du.

08:13.860 --> 08:15.060
Xu is a chosen candidate

08:15.060 --> 08:16.700
for a Chief Councillor by Chancellor Du.

08:17.420 --> 08:18.780
Now that he's won merit,

08:19.260 --> 08:20.140
how could they let him

08:20.140 --> 08:21.500
return to court for investiture?

08:24.660 --> 08:25.700
A strife within the court?

08:27.980 --> 08:29.780
Must that cost

08:29.780 --> 08:31.260
the lives of 200,000 soldiers?

08:33.380 --> 08:34.380
Are these the people

08:35.700 --> 08:36.540
we swore to protect?

08:43.820 --> 08:45.060
Though they meant to kill me,

08:46.620 --> 08:47.460
these provisions

08:49.180 --> 08:50.620
were not solely Marshal Qin's fault.

08:53.070 --> 08:54.280
Before the Liangzhou massacre,

08:54.746 --> 08:56.595
Qingsheng noticed
that the Ministry of Revenue

08:56.606 --> 08:57.980
had sent mixed grain with husks.

08:58.540 --> 08:59.860
Marshal Qin was furious,

09:00.380 --> 09:01.813
but he dared not offend the Revenue.

09:02.060 --> 09:03.500
So he could only send

09:04.380 --> 09:05.420
that batch here to us.

09:06.020 --> 09:07.180
Put aside

09:07.180 --> 09:08.380
those schemes for now.

09:08.940 --> 09:09.820
What do we do now?

09:10.580 --> 09:11.500
What should we do?

09:11.860 --> 09:13.020
Must we make the troops

09:13.660 --> 09:15.780
eat sod mixed with yellow earth?

09:17.900 --> 09:19.166
Court matters stay at the court.

09:20.420 --> 09:21.260
These provisions

09:21.820 --> 09:22.780
can still be useful.

09:23.540 --> 09:24.380
Commandant Xia,

09:24.780 --> 09:25.782
sort out the edible grain

09:25.793 --> 09:26.540
at once.

09:27.180 --> 09:28.540
Send some to the people tonight

09:28.860 --> 09:29.700
to assure them.

09:30.780 --> 09:31.860
Rebag the rest.

09:32.020 --> 09:33.420
- Seal it in the storehouse.
- Yes.

09:33.420 --> 09:34.260
Captain Han,

09:34.820 --> 09:36.100
post guards to watch 24/7.

09:36.540 --> 09:37.380
Pass the order:

09:37.700 --> 09:38.655
Those who leak the news

09:38.666 --> 09:39.540
face military law.

09:40.220 --> 09:41.060
Yes.

09:42.380 --> 09:43.566
The Spring Festival is coming.

09:45.300 --> 09:46.140
No matter what,

09:47.740 --> 09:50.060
we must let Shuozhou's people
celebrate it at ease

09:50.620 --> 09:51.780
after 30 hard years.

09:53.220 --> 09:54.060
Yes.

09:56.220 --> 09:57.060
Come with me.

09:57.860 --> 09:58.700
Let's go.

10:10.060 --> 10:10.940
Did you hear?

10:11.260 --> 10:12.140
The Chong Army outside

10:12.420 --> 10:13.940
has our city surrounded.

10:15.260 --> 10:18.020
Who knows how many days
the grain will last?

10:18.020 --> 10:19.060
Luckily, yesterday,

10:19.060 --> 10:20.380
the Tabai Army sent out grain.

10:20.380 --> 10:21.230
How many for you?

10:21.230 --> 10:22.150
Two.

10:22.150 --> 10:23.400
Two, right? Alright.

10:25.220 --> 10:26.540
Look, they're still piping hot.

10:31.020 --> 10:31.860
Put that down.

10:31.860 --> 10:32.700
He Yan,

10:33.780 --> 10:35.900
why are you stealing steamed buns again?

10:36.060 --> 10:38.300
You're the daughter
of a great household.

10:38.540 --> 10:39.860
You really have no sense of shame.

10:39.860 --> 10:41.580
She hid in the Chong Army's arms

10:41.706 --> 10:42.980
while we were left with nothing.

10:43.130 --> 10:43.980
Exactly.

10:43.980 --> 10:45.020
Without the Chong Army,

10:45.020 --> 10:46.140
she has no one to shield her.

10:46.140 --> 10:47.740
She used to look so grand

10:47.740 --> 10:49.420
only by treading on us commoners.

10:49.620 --> 10:50.460
Serves her right.

10:52.340 --> 10:55.060
(Wanshun Tower)

10:58.340 --> 10:59.180
Fengyi.

11:02.460 --> 11:03.300
Great Ancestor,

11:04.100 --> 11:06.220
you've finally remembered me again.

11:06.850 --> 11:08.960
Tell me.
What does it feel like to be alive?

11:09.540 --> 11:10.380
To be alive?

11:11.340 --> 11:12.820
Well...

11:15.860 --> 11:17.393
It feels like taking the better share.

11:18.260 --> 11:20.060
The Hejia clan never lives long.

11:20.300 --> 11:21.380
From the moment I was born,

11:21.540 --> 11:23.380
my life began counting down.

11:23.980 --> 11:24.940
So,

11:25.860 --> 11:27.420
every morning when I wake up,

11:28.060 --> 11:29.433
it means I've gained one more day.

11:29.980 --> 11:31.340
Every Spring Festival's Eve

11:31.540 --> 11:32.460
marks a milestone

11:32.460 --> 11:33.500
in my life.

11:34.660 --> 11:35.820
Is being alive that good?

11:36.060 --> 11:37.380
Of course, Great Ancestor.

11:38.180 --> 11:39.140
Each extra day I live

11:39.340 --> 11:40.540
is one more day to feel

11:40.540 --> 11:42.100
all the things in this world.

11:42.540 --> 11:43.380
Great Ancestor,

11:43.380 --> 11:44.740
once you find the spell bearer

11:44.740 --> 11:45.760
and gain your five senses,

11:45.771 --> 11:46.661
perhaps you'll feel

11:46.672 --> 11:47.758
the joy of being alive too.

11:52.180 --> 11:53.380
Forgive me, Great Ancestor.

11:55.020 --> 11:56.740
I spoke out of turn.

11:59.290 --> 12:00.630
I've found the spell bearer.

12:01.580 --> 12:02.420
It's Duan Xu.

12:05.980 --> 12:06.820
What happened?

12:07.860 --> 12:09.060
The Spirit Pearl showed

12:09.060 --> 12:10.020
no response at all.

12:10.020 --> 12:10.860
Why suddenly...

12:12.380 --> 12:13.220
That day,

12:14.100 --> 12:15.833
he happened
to pass through my spirit body.

12:18.380 --> 12:19.220
Great Ancestor,

12:19.340 --> 12:20.220
will you trade

12:20.220 --> 12:21.540
five senses with him?

12:22.460 --> 12:23.500
Of course.

12:24.020 --> 12:25.400
But he'll get something in return.

12:26.340 --> 12:27.380
Handle one matter for me.

12:29.860 --> 12:30.900
Always at your service.

12:31.780 --> 12:32.820
Go and find the servants

12:33.047 --> 12:34.920
who served Duan Xu
before he returned to Nandu.

12:37.740 --> 12:38.580
Great Ancestor,

12:40.220 --> 12:42.220
you still suspect Duan Xu?

12:42.400 --> 12:44.260
I do not care who the real Duan Xu is,

12:45.540 --> 12:47.460
but I want to know who he is.

12:48.420 --> 12:49.340
Only then can I better

12:49.340 --> 12:50.300
strike a deal with him.

12:51.620 --> 12:52.460
Xiaoxiao.

12:56.020 --> 12:56.940
What are you doing?

12:57.740 --> 12:58.933
The Spring Festival is coming.

12:59.100 --> 13:00.220
My father told me before.

13:00.400 --> 13:01.380
When the festival comes,

13:01.380 --> 13:02.329
we set off firecrackers,

13:02.340 --> 13:03.980
post Door Gods and the Fu character,

13:03.991 --> 13:05.542
and draw protective circles with lime

13:05.553 --> 13:06.660
to avert disaster.

13:06.780 --> 13:07.735
Haven't you heard enough

13:07.746 --> 13:08.733
of battle sounds already?

13:10.860 --> 13:12.300
But it seems

13:12.300 --> 13:13.580
the fighting has stopped outside.

13:13.980 --> 13:14.909
The Chong Army must be

13:14.920 --> 13:15.900
afraid of the General,

13:15.900 --> 13:16.846
so they dare not attack.

13:18.020 --> 13:18.940
If he truly were

13:18.940 --> 13:19.980
feared by all,

13:20.300 --> 13:22.020
he wouldn't be in this plight now.

13:24.140 --> 13:25.620
You laze about all day.

13:25.620 --> 13:27.123
You must be haunted by an evil spirit.

13:27.220 --> 13:28.320
I'll box the evil spirit in,

13:28.500 --> 13:30.300
so you won't be so lazy.

13:32.180 --> 13:33.460
I've always been curious.

13:33.860 --> 13:35.500
Who first came up

13:35.500 --> 13:36.740
with such a heaven-sent notion?

13:45.300 --> 13:47.300
The elders all say so:

13:47.300 --> 13:48.940
Evil spirits fear firecrackers,

13:48.940 --> 13:49.820
the color red,

13:49.820 --> 13:50.660
the Door Gods,

13:50.820 --> 13:51.860
and lime powder.

13:55.100 --> 13:56.180
Could it be

13:56.980 --> 13:58.540
that evil spirits don't even know

13:58.540 --> 13:59.700
what color red is?

14:00.420 --> 14:01.620
Father was right.

14:01.900 --> 14:03.700
You finally got moving.

14:06.540 --> 14:07.820
Is your New Year's wish

14:07.820 --> 14:09.100
for me to move around?

14:09.860 --> 14:11.740
Well, that's one of them.

14:12.020 --> 14:13.380
I have lots of wishes.

14:14.140 --> 14:15.020
For example,

14:15.020 --> 14:15.940
I want to stay with you

14:15.940 --> 14:16.940
forever and always.

14:17.100 --> 14:18.786
I want the General
to beat the Chong Army.

14:19.820 --> 14:21.260
And I want meat pie for every meal.

14:24.860 --> 14:26.660
What would he wish for?

14:27.780 --> 14:28.900
Xiaoxiao, what did you say?

14:30.180 --> 14:31.540
Your General.

14:32.700 --> 14:34.340
What do you think

14:34.340 --> 14:35.180
his wish would be?

14:35.820 --> 14:37.220
What would he want?

14:38.660 --> 14:40.700
I think it would be

14:41.820 --> 14:43.220
to eat eight meat pies

14:43.420 --> 14:44.460
in one meal.

14:45.900 --> 14:46.750
That doesn't sound

14:46.760 --> 14:47.600
like Duan Xu's wish.

14:47.740 --> 14:48.786
It sounds more like yours.

14:50.900 --> 14:51.780
Xiaoxiao,

14:52.340 --> 14:53.340
why are you asking

14:53.340 --> 14:54.820
about the General's wish?

14:57.940 --> 14:59.060
Because

15:00.060 --> 15:01.820
I want to make a very important deal

15:02.700 --> 15:04.180
with your General.

15:05.100 --> 15:05.980
I have to know him

15:06.660 --> 15:08.180
before I know how to bid.

15:08.820 --> 15:09.660
Xiaoxiao,

15:09.670 --> 15:10.740
are you feeling shy?

15:12.660 --> 15:13.500
What?

15:14.490 --> 15:15.380
Do you perhaps

15:15.380 --> 15:16.660
like the General?

15:17.900 --> 15:20.420
Last time, I heard you tell

15:20.940 --> 15:22.340
Captain Meng that for the General,

15:23.780 --> 15:24.900
it was love at first sight.

15:26.180 --> 15:27.220
Yes, yes, yes.

15:27.900 --> 15:29.020
Now that I think of it,

15:29.700 --> 15:31.540
Duan Xu and I truly are

15:32.020 --> 15:33.140
a match

15:34.100 --> 15:35.100
made by heaven.

15:35.700 --> 15:36.540
Xiaoxiao,

15:36.540 --> 15:38.260
you really have feelings
for the General?

15:38.900 --> 15:39.780
Xiaoxiao,

15:39.780 --> 15:40.740
we still have Ruan.

15:41.420 --> 15:42.620
You play so beautifully.

15:42.780 --> 15:44.460
Do you truly mean to play
for the General

15:44.460 --> 15:45.460
only at his funeral?

15:46.260 --> 15:47.740
Miss He will play at my funeral?

15:48.800 --> 15:49.660
General,

15:49.660 --> 15:50.580
when did you get here?

15:51.420 --> 15:52.260
Just now.

15:52.940 --> 15:53.900
I think I arrived

15:53.900 --> 15:54.820
when I heard

15:54.980 --> 15:56.220
"a match made by heaven".

15:58.340 --> 15:59.660
A perfect match indeed.

16:00.860 --> 16:02.340
You've even arranged

16:02.700 --> 16:03.900
what happens after I'm buried.

16:05.260 --> 16:06.700
I only fear my beloved General

16:06.700 --> 16:08.300
might suffer on his final road.

16:10.620 --> 16:11.460
Miss He,

16:12.340 --> 16:13.740
once Shuozhou is relieved,

16:15.020 --> 16:16.260
would you play a tune for me?

16:17.740 --> 16:18.580
No, that won't do.

16:19.160 --> 16:20.910
This tune is for the dying.

16:21.380 --> 16:22.380
If the living hear it,

16:22.700 --> 16:23.586
it brings ill fortune.

16:30.460 --> 16:32.020
What lovely plum blossoms.

16:34.780 --> 16:36.140
Your exquisite drawing skills

16:36.500 --> 16:37.540
look like they're

16:38.500 --> 16:39.860
from a master trained for decades.

16:42.540 --> 16:43.460
(That much is true.)

16:44.140 --> 16:45.580
(I have trained for centuries.)

16:47.020 --> 16:48.495
(Shuozhou)
I wonder when the General

16:48.506 --> 16:49.480
will send grain again.

16:49.480 --> 16:51.620
When will these hard days end?

16:51.620 --> 16:58.620
(Liang)

17:02.940 --> 17:03.780
You're here.

17:05.300 --> 17:06.900
You must already have a plan

17:07.980 --> 17:08.900
to deal

17:08.900 --> 17:09.940
with the coming

17:10.540 --> 17:11.740
Hulan Force siege.

17:12.660 --> 17:13.660
From what I saw today,

17:14.620 --> 17:15.760
lime powder would work well.

17:16.340 --> 17:17.340
Burning rainwater

17:17.351 --> 17:19.533
is the second punishment
in the Aphorisms of Cangshen.

17:19.940 --> 17:20.780
Do you think

17:21.780 --> 17:23.940
there will be an east wind
and rain soon?

17:24.940 --> 17:26.500
I am no master of wind and rain.

17:26.740 --> 17:27.895
I can't make whatever weather

17:27.906 --> 17:29.180
you want appear on command.

17:36.220 --> 17:37.500
The weather is dry and clear.

17:38.540 --> 17:39.420
It will not rain.

17:42.020 --> 17:42.860
What a pity.

17:43.900 --> 17:45.340
You are the General.

17:45.340 --> 17:46.700
Why think of such crooked ways?

17:49.060 --> 17:50.326
North Chong has 200,000 troops.

17:51.020 --> 17:52.020
I have less than 20,000.

17:53.020 --> 17:54.140
If we face them head-on,

17:55.100 --> 17:56.060
we'll be doomed.

18:00.100 --> 18:01.220
All mortals are suffering.

18:02.580 --> 18:03.580
All these conflicts

18:03.900 --> 18:05.340
are just quarrels on a snail's horn.

18:06.340 --> 18:07.380
So are we.

18:08.620 --> 18:09.580
A person's life

18:11.260 --> 18:12.540
is truly brief and small

18:13.460 --> 18:14.540
yet pitifully humble.

18:16.220 --> 18:17.060
Isn't that so?

18:18.100 --> 18:19.140
Why do you smile so much?

18:19.940 --> 18:20.780
I was born this way.

18:21.860 --> 18:23.500
Were you born to court death too?

18:26.140 --> 18:27.380
Why do you say that?

18:28.820 --> 18:30.660
The Chong Army will soon attack again.

18:30.973 --> 18:32.019
Even if you hold the line,

18:32.153 --> 18:33.180
with your remaining grain,

18:33.180 --> 18:34.220
how long can it last?

18:35.060 --> 18:36.820
You are a Chief Councillor candidate.

18:37.500 --> 18:38.340
If you die,

18:38.820 --> 18:39.860
all this glory and wealth

18:39.860 --> 18:41.420
will vanish in an instant.

18:42.660 --> 18:43.500
General,

18:43.740 --> 18:45.580
why stake your life on this?

18:48.220 --> 18:49.380
You make a very fair point.

18:53.060 --> 18:54.540
I can help you achieve great merits

18:54.618 --> 18:55.867
and leave your mark on history.

18:55.940 --> 18:57.780
I can let you enjoy rank and riches.

18:58.780 --> 18:59.620
I think

18:59.940 --> 19:00.980
even you

19:01.540 --> 19:02.659
would find such temptations

19:02.860 --> 19:04.220
hard to turn down.

19:05.820 --> 19:06.700
Or perhaps

19:06.700 --> 19:08.380
is there something you truly want?

19:11.260 --> 19:12.700
I want the Chong Army destroyed.

19:13.700 --> 19:14.760
I want the 17 Prefectures

19:15.260 --> 19:16.906
and the Guanhe River
all under Great Liang.

19:17.500 --> 19:18.766
I want peace across the realm,

19:19.540 --> 19:20.460
with war gone forever.

19:23.020 --> 19:23.860
Can you grant

19:24.620 --> 19:25.700
all this?

19:27.340 --> 19:28.420
Then you'll hear

19:29.860 --> 19:31.380
my Ruan melody very soon.

20:01.540 --> 20:02.620
Why have you come?

20:03.380 --> 20:04.293
Greetings, Your Grace.

20:05.140 --> 20:06.780
I have put Shao Yinyin to death.

20:07.620 --> 20:09.220
But I sheltered her,

20:09.220 --> 20:10.100
so I am guilty.

20:10.820 --> 20:12.380
I came to report and take blame.

20:12.620 --> 20:13.820
But you don't accept that.

20:16.420 --> 20:17.260
Your Grace,

20:17.820 --> 20:18.700
I only feel

20:18.700 --> 20:20.300
that you favor mortals too much.

20:20.420 --> 20:21.980
Yinyin's only obsession as a spirit

20:21.980 --> 20:23.140
was to have offspring.

20:23.500 --> 20:24.853
She longed for children by nature.

20:25.200 --> 20:26.060
Yet you forbade her

20:26.060 --> 20:27.500
from touching children under ten.

20:27.500 --> 20:28.740
That was simply impossible.

20:30.220 --> 20:31.180
For spirits to hunt

20:32.220 --> 20:33.580
is in their very nature.

20:33.580 --> 20:34.420
It is only natural.

20:35.300 --> 20:37.220
Why must you interfere so much?

20:37.220 --> 20:38.740
That is unreasonable.

20:38.900 --> 20:39.740
Reasonable?

20:44.460 --> 20:45.580
Reasonable?

20:48.580 --> 20:50.380
Do you think I became

20:52.020 --> 20:53.740
the Sovereign of Spirits by reason?

21:06.540 --> 21:07.380
Are you enraged?

21:08.460 --> 21:09.300
Are you in despair?

21:11.060 --> 21:12.340
Why am I allowed

21:12.340 --> 21:13.900
to shame you, break you,

21:14.100 --> 21:15.380
and toy with you

21:15.380 --> 21:16.220
as I please?

21:18.660 --> 21:19.780
Those who were slain

21:19.780 --> 21:21.380
thought the same before they died.

21:22.980 --> 21:24.460
What counts as only right?

21:25.100 --> 21:26.300
Jiang Ai covets wealth.

21:26.740 --> 21:27.860
Yan Ke is drawn to power.

21:28.420 --> 21:29.580
Guan Huai clings to life.

21:29.580 --> 21:30.620
You want fame and gain,

21:30.620 --> 21:31.460
yearning for rank.

21:32.060 --> 21:33.580
If spirits have no restraint,

21:34.980 --> 21:36.380
if desire knows no bounds,

21:37.300 --> 21:39.300
it is the deepest abyss of all.

21:52.580 --> 21:54.420
I was short-sighted.

21:55.260 --> 21:56.100
Go.

21:56.940 --> 21:58.020
Don't bother me these days.

22:26.260 --> 22:27.100
It is a black cat.

22:32.700 --> 22:33.540
Catch it.

22:37.660 --> 22:38.500
There! There! There!

22:38.860 --> 22:39.700
There!

22:44.900 --> 22:45.940
- General.
- General.

22:58.340 --> 22:59.180
General.

22:59.900 --> 23:00.740
It may be a trap.

23:23.340 --> 23:24.180
Han,

23:24.620 --> 23:25.900
what does it say? I can't read.

23:25.900 --> 23:27.160
(Cowards cross the Guanhe River.)

23:28.660 --> 23:31.300
Cowards cross the Guanhe River.

23:31.540 --> 23:33.580
Cowards cross the Guanhe River.

23:33.580 --> 23:34.620
Han, don't bother.

23:34.620 --> 23:35.660
It can't be anything good.

23:35.660 --> 23:37.060
Like 20,000 turtles sharing a den.

23:37.380 --> 23:39.860
Like 20,000 turtles sharing a den.

23:40.140 --> 23:41.420
You mangy curs.

23:41.620 --> 23:43.260
Sooner or later, we'll wipe you out.

23:44.700 --> 23:46.580
Like 20,000 turtles sharing a den.

23:46.580 --> 23:47.946
It's said that in the Hulan Force,

23:48.340 --> 23:50.300
only Marshal Awo'erqi keeps a black cat.

23:51.140 --> 23:51.980
That man

23:52.500 --> 23:53.580
must be Awo'erqi.

23:54.300 --> 23:56.700
Like 20,000 turtles sharing a den.

23:57.140 --> 24:00.140
Like 20,000 turtles sharing a den.

24:00.380 --> 24:02.820
Cowards cross the Guanhe River.

24:02.980 --> 24:05.900
Cowards cross the Guanhe River.

24:06.940 --> 24:08.340
They fled before the fight began.

24:13.620 --> 24:16.380
(Spring Comes to All Things)

24:16.660 --> 24:17.820
Here, child. Hold it tight.

24:18.100 --> 24:19.060
Thank you, sir.

24:24.100 --> 24:25.300
There is more. Have a look.

24:26.500 --> 24:27.340
Xiaoxiao,

24:27.460 --> 24:28.820
let's go buy some New Year's goods.

24:29.020 --> 24:30.580
The Spring Festival is in two days.

24:30.900 --> 24:31.980
Let's go find the General

24:31.980 --> 24:33.413
and spend the Spring Festival's Eve.

24:33.700 --> 24:34.740
Do you have any money?

24:41.340 --> 24:42.180
No.

24:45.940 --> 24:47.020
Here's my stipend.

24:47.700 --> 24:48.780
Buy whatever you like.

24:49.540 --> 24:50.700
Xiaoxiao,

24:50.700 --> 24:51.740
you're far too kind.

24:51.980 --> 24:52.820
I want to buy the one

24:52.820 --> 24:53.660
I saw just now.

24:54.090 --> 24:54.930
The round one.

24:54.940 --> 24:55.860
And candied hawthorns.

24:56.060 --> 24:56.980
And meat pie too.

24:56.980 --> 24:57.860
I'll buy them all.

24:58.060 --> 24:58.900
Come on.

24:59.660 --> 25:00.500
All right.

25:03.300 --> 25:04.780
(Shuozhou)

25:05.540 --> 25:06.380
Xiaoxiao,

25:06.540 --> 25:07.940
you're missing the General again?

25:10.700 --> 25:11.540
Yes, yes.

25:11.740 --> 25:12.980
I can't eat or drink at ease.

25:12.980 --> 25:14.740
One day apart feels like years.

25:20.060 --> 25:21.580
These Chong people are hateful.

25:22.140 --> 25:23.870
They make a racket at the gate daily.

25:29.580 --> 25:30.780
They're insulting us again.

25:31.180 --> 25:32.140
Yeah.

25:32.140 --> 25:33.780
Will they really start a fight?

25:39.180 --> 25:42.180
(Shuozhou)

25:42.180 --> 25:43.580
The General is on the city wall.

25:43.700 --> 25:44.540
It's fine.

25:44.980 --> 25:45.820
Don't be afraid.

25:45.820 --> 25:46.860
They're just bluffing.

25:47.120 --> 25:48.010
They've come

25:48.010 --> 25:48.910
to shout several times.

25:49.300 --> 25:50.460
Nothing has really happened.

25:50.460 --> 25:51.300
Exactly.

25:52.186 --> 25:53.562
With the General here, we're safe.

25:53.620 --> 25:54.460
Come again next time.

25:54.620 --> 25:55.460
Let's go.

25:57.580 --> 25:58.540
You go buy it yourself.

25:58.700 --> 25:59.820
I'm going to the wall.

26:14.380 --> 26:16.860
(Shuozhou)

26:30.220 --> 26:31.220
Duan Shunxi!

26:31.820 --> 26:33.780
You timid, pretty boy!

26:34.680 --> 26:35.540
You must be scared

26:35.540 --> 26:36.660
of me here.

26:37.060 --> 26:38.140
That's why you hide

26:38.380 --> 26:39.380
in the city.

26:39.820 --> 26:40.860
Come out and fight us

26:40.860 --> 26:41.860
if you dare.

26:42.180 --> 26:43.020
Just watch me

26:43.300 --> 26:44.980
beat your head bloody

26:44.980 --> 26:46.420
till you cry for mercy.

26:48.180 --> 26:49.373
They've been cursing for days.

26:51.500 --> 26:52.420
They insult you

26:52.580 --> 26:53.860
to lure you out to fight.

26:54.380 --> 26:55.580
Are they insulting me?

26:56.420 --> 26:57.460
From another angle,

26:57.460 --> 26:58.520
they're praising my looks.

26:58.940 --> 26:59.780
I appreciate it.

27:01.980 --> 27:03.900
You truly are magnanimous.

27:03.900 --> 27:04.980
Most admirable indeed.

27:07.700 --> 27:08.580
By the way,

27:08.580 --> 27:09.660
just now, I think I saw

27:09.660 --> 27:10.500
a soldier

27:10.660 --> 27:11.822
heading toward the third tent

27:11.833 --> 27:12.980
at the far south.

27:12.980 --> 27:13.960
He was holding a letter.

27:14.660 --> 27:16.060
I could see the words on the cover,

27:16.060 --> 27:17.106
but I could not read them.

27:26.180 --> 27:27.020
Miss,

27:27.180 --> 27:28.073
please copy them down.

27:36.380 --> 27:37.300
Are you scared?

27:38.300 --> 27:39.500
Come out. Are you scared?

27:39.500 --> 27:40.980
Come out and face me in battle.

27:44.540 --> 27:45.940
So, you really can read that.

27:47.060 --> 27:47.940
This is an insult

27:48.940 --> 27:50.500
from the Aphorisms of Cangshen.

27:50.980 --> 27:51.820
It means something

27:51.820 --> 27:53.020
like a spineless cur.

27:53.700 --> 27:54.940
If you wished to scold me,

27:55.820 --> 27:57.100
there was no need for all this.

27:58.940 --> 28:00.940
How knowledgeable of you.

28:01.620 --> 28:02.900
Even the ancient texts

28:02.900 --> 28:03.860
make sense to you.

28:05.420 --> 28:06.580
That is a long story.

28:07.380 --> 28:08.460
One day, I met an old man

28:08.460 --> 28:09.333
who took off his shoe

28:09.344 --> 28:10.740
and tossed it beneath the bridge.

28:11.060 --> 28:12.740
He told me to fetch it
and put it on him.

28:13.300 --> 28:14.329
This happened three times.

28:14.340 --> 28:15.220
- Well.
- I...

28:15.220 --> 28:16.460
What a familiar tale.

28:17.140 --> 28:18.380
Was the book that the old man

28:18.900 --> 28:20.340
gave you Taigong's Art of War?

28:22.060 --> 28:23.360
It was the Aphorisms of Cangshen.

28:24.860 --> 28:26.660
I should go back
and check the chronicles.

28:26.820 --> 28:28.980
Perhaps they record your great deeds.

28:33.540 --> 28:34.380
I did have

28:35.180 --> 28:37.140
a formidable master from North Chong.

28:38.220 --> 28:39.620
I was his finest disciple.

28:44.820 --> 28:45.660
And where is he now?

28:46.780 --> 28:48.240
His eyes were pecked blind by geese.

28:48.966 --> 28:50.159
So he withdrew from the world.

28:51.180 --> 28:52.420
Duan Shunxi,

28:53.740 --> 28:55.180
you really change in a blink.

28:55.267 --> 28:56.300
No one can read your mind.

28:56.740 --> 28:58.060
Not one word from you is true.

28:58.060 --> 28:59.460
Did you truly see nothing just now?

29:01.300 --> 29:02.140
I did.

29:02.540 --> 29:03.226
I saw him go

29:03.237 --> 29:04.530
into the third camp on the left.

29:04.980 --> 29:05.940
But

29:05.940 --> 29:07.220
what he held was not a letter,

29:07.660 --> 29:08.860
but a few goldfish.

29:13.660 --> 29:14.756
The third camp on the left?

29:16.260 --> 29:17.100
That's right.

29:22.660 --> 29:23.500
You have sharp eyes.

29:24.420 --> 29:25.260
Many thanks.

29:28.020 --> 29:29.620
The granary is on fire!

29:33.100 --> 29:35.100
The granary is on fire!

29:35.620 --> 29:36.900
The granary is on fire!

29:37.420 --> 29:38.820
The granary is on fire.

29:39.780 --> 29:41.500
The granary is on fire.

29:41.500 --> 29:42.340
Right here. Hurry.

29:45.940 --> 29:46.780
It's burned.

29:46.940 --> 29:47.900
It's burned.

29:47.900 --> 29:48.740
It's all burned.

29:50.340 --> 29:52.060
It's burned. All of it.

29:52.660 --> 29:53.500
It's all burned.

29:54.940 --> 29:55.780
It's burned.

29:56.660 --> 29:57.793
- Madwoman.
- It's burned.

29:57.804 --> 29:58.700
What are you plotting?

29:58.700 --> 29:59.480
It's burned.

29:59.491 --> 30:00.449
- You did it.
- Burned.

30:00.460 --> 30:01.300
What will we eat now?

30:01.700 --> 30:02.540
It's all burned.

30:05.900 --> 30:07.100
It's burned. All of it.

30:07.660 --> 30:08.500
It's burned.

30:18.220 --> 30:19.260
It's all burned.

30:19.540 --> 30:20.533
I have failed in my duty.

30:20.660 --> 30:21.700
General, please punish me.

30:22.580 --> 30:23.480
How did the fire start?

30:24.380 --> 30:25.820
The woman outside set it on purpose.

30:26.060 --> 30:26.980
It started

30:26.980 --> 30:27.820
where the provisions

30:27.820 --> 30:28.866
were stacked the thickest.

30:30.779 --> 30:32.159
Get everyone to put it out at once.

30:32.780 --> 30:33.893
Do not let the people panic.

30:34.220 --> 30:35.060
Go.

30:35.340 --> 30:36.180
Yes.

30:39.460 --> 30:40.300
Quick.

30:40.620 --> 30:41.660
Quick, quick.

30:42.300 --> 30:44.340
Hurry up!

30:47.300 --> 30:48.340
The grain is gone!

30:48.860 --> 30:49.780
It is all burned!

30:49.780 --> 30:50.900
It has all burned down!

30:51.100 --> 30:52.300
The grain is gone!

30:52.500 --> 30:54.580
May you all starve! Starve!

30:54.580 --> 30:55.540
Who is that madwoman?

30:56.100 --> 30:57.740
- The top courtesan.
- You'll starve!

30:57.740 --> 30:59.010
- He Yan.
- May you all starve!

30:59.150 --> 31:00.820
If you hadn't driven off
the Chong people.

31:01.200 --> 31:02.520
Shame on her!

31:03.060 --> 31:04.740
I wouldn't have fallen this low.

31:06.500 --> 31:07.780
Everyone in Shuozhou

31:07.780 --> 31:09.420
deserves to die.

31:09.420 --> 31:10.430
What nonsense.

31:10.740 --> 31:12.020
Beat her. Beat her to death.

31:12.020 --> 31:13.900
Hit her. Beat her to death.

31:17.180 --> 31:19.262
If you had the chance to cling
to the Chong people,

31:19.273 --> 31:19.820
wouldn't you?

31:20.020 --> 31:21.100
Wouldn't you?

31:22.380 --> 31:23.340
I did nothing wrong.

31:23.340 --> 31:24.740
I truly did nothing wrong.

31:24.740 --> 31:25.580
I didn't...

31:26.940 --> 31:27.780
Well done.

31:27.940 --> 31:29.100
With that mouth of hers,

31:30.540 --> 31:31.500
she had it coming.

31:34.340 --> 31:36.100
How did you fool the granary guards

31:37.660 --> 31:38.660
and get into the granary?

31:39.580 --> 31:40.780
What's wrong with the guards?

31:41.940 --> 31:44.300
Even the guards are men.

31:44.780 --> 31:45.860
Shameless wretch.

31:47.500 --> 31:49.620
(The General means to kill.)

31:51.020 --> 31:54.420
- Kill her.
- Kill her.

31:55.100 --> 31:57.940
You lofty people up there,

31:58.620 --> 32:00.020
you want me dead.

32:01.140 --> 32:02.140
If I must die,

32:02.820 --> 32:04.420
then we die together.

32:28.400 --> 32:33.730
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

32:34.060 --> 32:38.310
♪Light encountered shadow♪

32:39.670 --> 32:45.040
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

32:45.340 --> 32:49.940
♪The unbreakable fate♪

32:51.030 --> 32:52.870
♪Suddenly cracked♪

33:05.080 --> 33:10.520
♪Between black and white,
ripples crossed♪

33:10.700 --> 33:15.030
♪Light encountered shadow♪

33:16.400 --> 33:21.790
♪It pierced the darkness and the time♪

33:22.020 --> 33:25.960
♪The unbreakable fate♪

33:27.730 --> 33:29.620
♪Suddenly cracked♪

33:32.280 --> 33:35.440
♪Listen, all sounds are roaring♪

33:35.440 --> 33:37.970
♪As cold ice turns into tides♪

33:37.970 --> 33:43.490
♪A century's loneliness melts dreams♪

33:43.490 --> 33:46.730
♪Following fate's guidance♪

33:46.730 --> 33:51.590
♪By fate, our moments were exchanged♪

33:51.930 --> 33:54.950
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪

33:54.950 --> 33:57.770
♪Watch fireworks fall like stars♪

33:58.030 --> 34:00.560
♪This bond is tangled into a thread♪

34:00.560 --> 34:05.980
♪Worldly reflections fade into mist♪

34:06.150 --> 34:09.220
♪Borrowing one fleeting heartbeat♪

34:09.380 --> 34:14.280
♪You drew me into mortal dust,
till I'm enamored with its charms♪

34:14.490 --> 34:17.960
♪The heart wakes up all of a sudden♪
